sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Compose UI
    participant VM as ViewModel
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DAO as Room DAO
    participant DB as SQLite DB

    Note over User,DB: Mark Worker Attendance
    User->>UI: Tap attendance chip (Present/Half/Absent)
    UI->>VM: markAttendance(workerId, value)
    VM->>Repo: insertLaborEntry(LaborEntry)
    Repo->>DAO: laborEntryDao.insert(entry)
    DAO->>DB: INSERT INTO labor_entries
    DB-->>DAO: rowId
    DAO-->>Repo: success
    Repo-->>VM: coroutine complete
    VM->>VM: StateFlow emits updated workerStates
    VM-->>UI: recompose WorkerCard

    Note over User,DB: Add New Site
    User->>UI: Fill name + tap "Use My Location"
    UI->>UI: GPS / Geocoder resolves address
    User->>UI: Tap "Save Site"
    UI->>Repo: insertSite(Site)
    Repo->>DAO: siteDao.insert(site)
    DAO->>DB: INSERT INTO sites
    DB-->>DAO: siteId
    DAO-->>Repo: success
    Repo-->>UI: navigate to Photos tab

    Note over User,DB: Load Material Rates (startup seed)
    UI->>Repo: getAllMaterialRates().first()
    Repo->>DAO: materialRateDao.getAllRates()
    DAO->>DB: SELECT * FROM material_rates
    DB-->>DAO: List empty?
    DAO-->>Repo: emptyList
    Repo->>DAO: insert default rates (Brick/Cement/Sand)
    DAO->>DB: INSERT INTO material_rates
